snippet.title: Zooconomy Gameplay Trailer (PC, strategy-puzzle)
snippet.description:
Zooconomy - strategy-puzzle game where you exchange animals. 

Animals are you currency. 
Breed, Exchange, Repeat.

Complete historic based story missions or play in sandbox. Get animals, breed them, attract visitors, sponsor expeditions for unique animals, upgrade zoo and much more.

Coming for PC in 2020 and later for Mobile and Nintendo Switch.

Trailer music: www.bensound.com

Join our Discord channel: https://discord.gg/uhhXqXCpyf
Follow us in Twitter: https://twitter.com/cur_foxes
Follow us in VK: https://vk.com/curiousfoxes
Add Zooconomy to the wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1358110/Zooconomy/
